cwThree

Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cwThree.Customer

  • public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates a customer object with current floor and destination floor details, based on those values status of the object is also set such as whether current floor is 13 or whether they have reached their destination. Default is - customerID = 0 currentFloor = 0 destinationFloor = 0 inElevator = false finished = false
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ronu Miah
